name: Hollow Pixels 19 - Ant
description:
This creature doesn’t know it has been named « Ant », nor does it know what an ant is. 
Looking at it, we can assume Ant is probably devastated in front of such a challenge. Because when one doesn’t know or forgot what they are, the simple things seem impossible.
Or it might just as well be safe in its nest.
